## 3. Report – detailed file (smart) + Playwright-only scope

- **Problem:** Report contained cross-deps-only narrative; Slack was too long. Users want **full traceability on disk** and a **short Slack** summary.
- **Rule:** The HandsOff report **`HandsOff reports/YYYY/<english-month>/<DD>/{JIRA_KEY}.md`** MUST follow **`Cursor-Project/config/playwright/Playwright_run_detailed_report_template.md`**: run metadata; **per executed test** — Playwright title, **TC-BE-N / TC-FE-N** covered (from test titles + **`test_cases/`** `.md` from the flow), **created entity links or ids**, **expected** (from TC), **actual**, **meets expectation** (Yes/No/Not run).
- **Rule:** Do not fill the report with cross-dependency dumps or unrelated artifact lists. Include spec path and command in the header section of the template.

Reference: Rule 37; **`Cursor-Project/config/playwright/Playwright_run_detailed_report_template.md`**; `.cursor/commands/hands-off.md` Step 6.

