- **Artifact:** **`Cursor-Project/EnergoTS/playwright-report-detailed.md`** from **`generate-detailed-report.mjs`** + **`EnergoTS/playwright-report.json`** (Jira + TC id + scenario parsed from `test()` title when titled `[KEY] TC-BE-n: …`, step titles, annotations, per-test outcomes).
